query:
UPDATE ingredient_stock_moves
        SET name = $1,
            ingredient_catalog_uuid = $2,
            quantity = $3,
            price = $4,
            price_updated_at = $5,
            effective_at = $6,
            expiry_at = $7,
            ref_type = $8,
            ref_uuid = $9,
            unit_of_measure_code = $10,
            unit_of_measure_name = $11,
            updated_at = $12
        WHERE uuid = $13 AND deleted_at = 0
        RETURNING uuid,
                  name,
                  ingredient_catalog_uuid,
                  quantity,
                  price,
                  price_updated_at,
                  effective_at,
                  expiry_at,
                  ref_type,
                  ref_uuid,
                  unit_of_measure_code,
                  unit_of_measure_name,
                  created_at,
                  updated_at
